headline: Couche-Tard Keeps Pushing to Buy Seven & i, Sees US Approval
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Canadian convenience store operator Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. will keep up “friendly and persistent” attempts to forge a deal to acquire Seven & i Holdings Co., saying that it has financing in place and sees a clear path to gaining antitrust regulatory approval in the US.
